ir livelihood, money and fame lying and spreading falsehoo=\r\nds about Hinduism, Hindu deities and Hindu saints.&lt;BR&gt;&lt;BR&gt;Those who are not=\r\n inclined to fight a dharma yuddha against this may ignore this and go on d=\r\noing their sadhana. After all, if enough people do sadhana to strengthen sa=\r\nnatana dharma, this kind of things will automatically weaken. However, some=\r\n scholars engaging these pseudo-scholars academically is really required on=\r\n the ground. We need to give our encouragement to the pioneers who are doin=\r\ng this important scholarly rebuttal.&lt;BR&gt;&lt;BR&gt;Best regards,&lt;BR&gt;Narasimha&lt;BR&gt;-=\r\n---------------------------------------------------------&lt;BR&gt;Free Jyotish S=\r\noftware, Free Jyotish MP3 Lessons, Free Jyotish textbook,&lt;BR&gt;Free &quot;Do It Yo=\r\nurself&quot; ritual manuals for short Homam and Pitri Tarpana:&lt;BR&gt;&lt;SPAN&gt;&lt;A href=\r\n=3D&quot;http://www.vedicastrologer.org/&quot; rel=3Dnofollow target=3D_blank&gt;http://=\r\nwww.VedicAstrologer.org&lt;/A&gt;&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;BR&gt;&lt;SPAN&gt;Films that make a difference: &lt;=\r\nA\n href=3D&quot;http://saraswatifilms.org/&quot; rel=3Dnofollow target=3D_blank&gt;http:=\r\n//SaraswatiFilms.org&lt;/A&gt;&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;BR&gt;&lt;SPAN&gt;Spirituality: &lt;A href=3D&quot;http://gr=\r\noups.yahoo.com/group/vedic-wisdom&quot; rel=3Dnofollow target=3D_blank&gt;http://gr=\r\noups.yahoo.com/group/vedic-wisdom&lt;/A&gt;&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;BR&gt;&lt;SPAN&gt;Jyotish writings: &lt;A =\r\nhref=3D&quot;http://groups.yahoo.com/group/JyotishWritings&quot; rel=3Dnofollow targe=\r\nt=3D_blank&gt;http://groups.yahoo.com/group/JyotishWritings&lt;/A&gt;&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;BR&gt;----=\r\n------------------------------------------------------&lt;BR&gt;&lt;BR&gt;&lt;/P&gt;&lt;/DIV&gt;&lt;/D=\r\nIV&gt;&lt;/DIV&gt;&lt;/DIV&gt;&lt;/DIV&gt;&lt;/DIV&gt;&lt;BR&gt;\n&lt;P&gt;&lt;/P&gt;&lt;/DIV&gt;\n&lt;DIV style=3D&quot;COLOR: #fff&quot;&gt;&lt;/=\r\nDIV&gt;&lt;/DI